Connection, Growth
Every service – from personal
coaching to couples counselling – is
geared towards creating clarity,
strengthening relationships, and
sustaining growth in clients’ lives
and careers.
Integrated & Accessible Services
A fully online practice offering 1:1, couples, and group programs, with
specialized support (e.g. ADHD membership) and easy digital tools to keep
clients engaged and supported between sessions.
Services & Target Audiences
Coach4U offers a comprehensive suite of coaching and counselling services
tailored to different client needs and contexts. Key offerings include individual
(personal) coaching, couples coaching/counselling, an ADHD group coaching
membership, business & leadership coaching, and career coaching 1 4
. Each
service is designed with specific target audiences and goals in mind, as
summarized below:
